snippet.title: Best VGM 1362 - Ys Origin - Genesis Beyond the Beginning
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1830 - https://youtu.be/Xw58jPitU-Q

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Ys Origin (2007)
Genesis Beyond the Beginning
Hayato Sonoda, Takahiro Unisuga & Ryo Takeshita
